reviewText: If I could give a 10 Star, I would surely give it to this series!!! Oh my! I cannot stop watching it. It is amazing. It will fill you with love, make you angry, make you hate, and then learn to love again. You will never regret watching this series!!! Please get it without hesitation. This is not a promotion. I am not even sure how I found it but was looking into watching a good Filipino series and I tried this. Fell in love with it as soon as I started. I am not Filipino but can watch this over and over and over again. YOU WILL LOVE IT!!!
